v 3
d googlesheets. Read, write, and edit Google Sheets directly from Stata.
d
d googlesheets mirrors the import excel / export excel / putexcel family,
d but talks to live Google Sheets via the Sheets API.  Surgical placement
d of values and matrices, on-demand cell formatting, sheet (tab)
d management, and filtered reads of Google Forms response sheets.
d
d Subcommands:
d   import, export, put, format, list, ping,
d   addsheet, deletesheet, renamesheet.
d
d Requires: Stata 17+, Python 3 on PATH, an OAuth 2.0 Desktop client JSON
d (one-time GCP setup; see README).  The package creates a private Python
d venv on first run and installs the Google client libraries into it.
d
d KW: google sheets
d KW: spreadsheets
d KW: import
d KW: export
d KW: putexcel
d KW: api
d KW: oauth
d KW: forms
d
d Author: Eric A. Booth, Sr Researcher, Texas2036.org
d Support: eric.a.booth@gmail.com
